headline: Lennar Corporation Declares Quarterly Dividends
summary: Lennar Corporation (NYSE: LEN and LEN.B), one of the nation's leading homebuilders, announced that its Board of Directors has declared a quarterly cash dividend of $0.50 per share for both Class A and Class B common stock payable on May 7, 2025 to holders of record at the close of business on April 23, 2025.

headline: Weekly Picks: ? Lennar's Recovery, Saudi Aramco's Yield, and SSAB's Prime Tariff Positioning
summary: This week’s picks cover: What SSAB stands to gain from trade tensions, surging EU demand, and a weak krona. Why long-term tailwinds and a cheap valuation make Lennar one to watch. Plus, how Saudi Aramco’s yield and clout make it a bond-like bet on global stability.
